ends find the courage to be their true selves in a story about empathy and growth.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106830/extras/060ba18ac7dcbdbe2b6147fd91000260.poster.avif?t=1745413687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106830/extras/060ba18ac7dcbdbe2b6147fd91000260.webm?t=1745413687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1106830/extras/060ba18ac7dcbdbe2b6147fd91000260.mp4?t=1745413687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
